Type Fast Game: Test your writing speed!

INTRODUCTION
Type Fast is the best free massively multiplayer online competitive typing game.

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Type Fast extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Type Fast icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Type Fast popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!
